# Managing Basic Network

hostname or hostnamectl hostname command line can be use to change our hostname

ex: hostname rhcsa.example.com
hostname will change root@localhost -> root@rhcsa.example.com

# NetWorkManager and tools
NetWorkManager is default network management service in RHEl system.

nmcli: Network manager command line interface
nmtui: Network Manager test user interface
nm-connection-editor: Graphical user interface
